| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4413 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e7a3b939-bb82-5d9d-98e8-5e6279cebcca"
